'''奧爾堡塔'''（Aalborgtårnet）是位於[[丹麥|丹麥]]城市[[奧爾堡|奧爾堡]]的一座瞭望塔，高54.9米。奧爾堡塔修建在一座山上，算上山峰高度的話則總高度是105米<ref name="PorterPrince2011">{{cite book|last1=Porter|first1=Darwin|last2=Prince|first2=Danforth|last3=Norum|first3=Roger|title=Frommer's Scandinavia|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=NEcXtIx2ZPEC&pg=PT172|date=15 June 2011|publisher=John Wiley & Sons|isbn=978-1-118-09023-7|page=172|access-date=2016-02-04|archive-date=2014-07-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140707000833/http://books.google.com/books?id=NEcXtIx2ZPEC&pg=PT172|dead-url=no}}</ref>。塔頂有一個餐廳。奧爾堡塔竣工於1933年<ref name="Birket-Smithkunstmuseum2002">{{cite book|last=Birket-Smith|first=Thomas|title=Fabrik: industriens arkitektur i Aalborg|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=OSRUAAAAMAAJ|year=2002|publisher=Fonden til udgivelse af Arkitekturtidsskrift B|language=da|page=78|access-date=2016-02-04|archive-date=2014-07-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140707001149/http://books.google.com/books?id=OSRUAAAAMAAJ|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

